node.text: May God protect these workers who have been doing most of the tough n dangerous jobs for our Singaporeans.. Take good care..

The new cases announced by the Ministry of Health bring the total number of cases here to 1,623.

It is the highest single-day spike of cases here, the previous being the 120 cases reported on Sunday (April 5). #linkinbio to learn more.
